msgctxt "#30052"
msgid "Enter the full LibreTranslate URL starting with http:// or https://. Example: http://192.168.x.x:5000 . Make sure your server loaded the needed languages, for example LT_LOAD_ONLY=en,ro. Batch limit also matters: set LT_BATCH_LIMIT above your selected chunk size. 1000 is a good setting."
msgstr ""

